text: Elanne Starlight is a 2016 Chinese romantic drama film directed by Wang Ziqi and starring Elanne Kong, Lu Yulin, Ye Xinchen, Chen Zeyu, Joe Ma, Anne Heung and Sze Yu. It was released in China by Pearl River Pictures on August 26, 2016. ==Plot== ==Cast== *Elanne Kong *Lu Yulin *Ye Xinchen *Chen Zeyu *Joe Ma *Anne Heung *Sze Yu *Zhong Kai *Wu Jinxi ==Reception== The film grossed at the Chinese box office. ==References== Category:Chinese films Category:Chinese romantic drama films Category:2016 romantic drama films Category:2016 drama films
